Interface MethodLookupEngine.Finding

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MethodLookupEngine.Finding.Default, Morph.Binder.PrecomputedFinding, Pipe.Binder.PrecomputedFinding
    Enclosing interface:
    MethodLookupEngine

    public static interface MethodLookupEngine.Finding
    A finding contains a class's extracted invokable methods which were computed by a MethodLookupEngine.
